This repository is an eval-only extraction scaffold derived from the public
`python-dlshogi2` project by Tadao Yamaoka.

Upstream project:
  https://github.com/TadaoYamaoka/python-dlshogi2

Derived / adapted files in this scaffold:
  - src/dlshogi2_eval/features.py
  - src/dlshogi2_eval/model.py

The intent is to preserve the reference feature encoding and policy/value
network while removing training, MCTS, and engine-specific code.

Before publishing a frozen release, fill in `UPSTREAM_SNAPSHOT.md` with:
  - upstream repository URL
  - upstream commit hash
  - exact vendored paths
  - checkpoint artifact hash(es)
